reconstruct the 19 buildings on the list. 
</P>
<P>
 Ranked first and second were the Junipero Serra State Office Building on South 
Broadway and the Caltrans district office on Spring Street, both in Downtown 
Los Angeles and both recommended for demolition. The report also recommends 
demolition of the South Hill Street parking garage in Downtown Los Angeles and 
the San Diego State Office building on Front Street in San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
