minister and rabbi also will take part. President Clinton and the First Lady 
will attend. 
</P>
<P>
 There will be a post-wedding reception for the 250 guests, but the couple 
"haven't gotten to a menu yet, because the White House just changed chefs," the 
bride-to-be said. 
</P>
<P>
 "When you have events at the White House you are not allowed to bring food in 
from the outside, ever," she added. 
