this most evocative segment of the show suggested that old songs don't stop 
meaning something just because they are old. 
</P>
<P>
 * Pink Floyd plays tonight at 8 and Sunday at 7 p.m. at the Rose Bowl, 1001 
Rose Bowl Drive, Pasadena, (818) 577-3100. Tickets are still available for 
Sunday, $75 and $35.  
</P>
<P>
 * BIG PAYDAY: Pink Floyd joins other big-name acts in heating up the summer 
pop concerts. F7 
