<HEADLINE>
<P>
LETTERS ON KURT COBAIN; VOICE OF A GENERATION, OR A COWARD? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Just to numb ourselves in drug abuse would only increase the problems and pain 
of our lives. I pray that all people in our troubled world would find the inner 
comfort, strength, peace, joy and hope that only come from a good relationship 
with our heavenly maker. 
</P>
<P>
 DANIEL LIM 
</P>
<P>
 Westminster 
