<HEADLINE>
<P>
SURVEY OF ARTISTS SEEKING HEALTH PLAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 As part of its plan to establish a statewide group health plan for artists, 
the Artist's Alliance of California is asking that all artists statewide 
complete a survey to help implement such a plan. 
</P>
<P>
 The Santa Monica-based organization believes that the more completed surveys 
it receives, the stronger its bargaining position will be to obtain a low-cost 
health plan. 
</P>
<P>
 Participants do not need to be members of the Alliance to participate. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information, or to receive a copy of the survey, call (310) 450-5728. 
</P>
</TEXT>
