<TEXT>
<P>
 The last store to return to the Woodland Hills Promenade Mall after January's 
earthquake celebrates its official reopening today, three months after losing 
part of its wall and roof in the disaster. 
</P>
<P>
 The opening of the I. Magnin outlet at 6101 Owensmouth Ave. marks the end of 
the mall's repairs. 
</P>
