 Only the Saks Fifth Avenue store remains closed, Duke said, and there are no 
plans to reopen it. Elizabeth Pedersen-Knapp, marketing director for the mall, 
said the damage was too extensive and Saks doesn't want to invest in the 
repairs. KURT PITZER 
