 In the Academy League: 
</P>
<P>
 St. Margaret's 2, Lake Elsinore Cal Lutheran 1 -- Andy Koert had two hits, 
including a game-winning sixth-inning single, for visiting St. Margaret's (7-1, 
2-0). 
</P>
