 Victor Valley 4, Antelope Valley 2 -- Angelo Sakelarious, Frankie Maldonado, 
Derek Forman and J.P. Hamilton each had two hits for the Rams (10-10, 5-9) in a 
Foothill Conference game. Jack Cox was two for three and scored a run for 
Antelope Valley (11-12, 5-9). 
