<P>
 Misleading Headline-A headline in the West County Edition on Thursday, on a 
story concerning a deputy public defender's accusation of prosecutorial 
misconduct, might have been misleading.Deputy Dist. Atty. Terence M. Kilbride 
himself did not face the possibility of arrest or incarceration in connection 
with the complaint. A hearing before Superior Court Judge Charles W. Campbell 
Jr. was held only to determine whether there were grounds for granting a new 
trial in a case prosecuted by Kilbride. 
